TANK YOU VERY MUCH WOLOLO TANK was created/rendered by Thobie Buntaran a.k.a. Loreng on 12 October 2021, Mantrijeron, Yogyakarta, Indonesia.

 “We learn that humans in the past interact with & through machinery, this inspired us, Santuarians, to make something similar but out of context from its original purposes. We design a nonlethal weapon & machine to show our gratitude not only to allies but to enemies.
This Wololo Tank is the symbol of harmony & chaos. Tank You Very Much custom typeface crafted using rare materials, Uranium, a symbol of peace & democracy from Planet Earth.” - Valentin, Creative Director of Santuari Studio.
